name: Cyrce's Circlet
description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description: Equip: Taking damage has a chance to erupt the ground, covering you in a layer of dark oil that absorbs 553,993 damage for 15 sec. When the shield is broken, it splatters nearby enemies for 133,018 Shadow damage.

Equip: Your abilities have a very high chance to lash out with a Hateful Strike, inflicting 177,434 Physical damage to an enemy and healing you for 10,396. These effects are increased by 100% while you are below 35% health.
